name: Snaketreewood - Collar Stiffeners
description:
These solid snaketreewood collar stiffeners are made in Germany.
They come in a classy travel-box.
Available in three sizes:
S (2.13 X 0.43 in / 5,4 X 1,1 cm)
M (2.32 X 0.43 in / 5,9 X 1,1 cm)
L (2.52 X 0.43 in / 6,4 X 1,1 cm)

Please note:
Collar stiffeners made of natural materials should always be removed before cleaning and ironing.
Do not put pressure on them.
Keep out of reach of children.
-------------------------------------------
A.k.a. collar stays, collar bones, collar sticks, collar tabs.
